fields.title: I-65 Underpass
fields.description: A mysterious place where many diverse characters are known to gather

fields.title: Demonbreun Cave
fields.description: This cave starts out in the woods next to some kind of waste management facility and goes all the way out to a rocky cliff overlooking the Cumberland.  I heard that orignally some old fur trapper named Demonbreun used to live here?  People used to live in some weird places.

fields.title: Belle Island Zoo
fields.description: I was driving around Belle Island in Detroit when I saw a fenced area overgrown with ivy with strange looking structures behind it.  I crawled under the fence to look around and found it was an abandoned zoo.
